title: ContactPerson
description: The main individual to contact regarding the resource

title: DataCollector
description: Person responsible for collecting data.

title: DataCurator
description: Person responsible for managing and curating the data.

title: DataManager
description: Person responsible for maintaining the data.

title: Distributor
description: Entity that distributes the data.

title: Editor
description: Person responsible for overseeing the content's editorial aspects.

title: HostingInstitution
description: The institution hosting the data.

title: Producer
description: Person or organization responsible for producing the data.

title: ProjectLeader
description: Person who leads the project or study.

title: ProjectManager
description: Person responsible for managing the project's administrative aspects.

title: ProjectMember
description: Member of the project team.

title: RegistrationAgency
description: Agency responsible for registering the data.

title: RegistrationAuthority
description: Authority that oversees the registration process.

title: RelatedPerson
description: Person related to the data or study, but not directly contributing.

title: Researcher
description: Person who conducts the research.

title: ResearchGroup
description: A group of researchers working on the data or study.

title: RightsHolder
description: Entity holding the rights to the data.

title: Sponsor
description: Entity sponsoring the data or research.

title: Supervisor
description: Person supervising the research or project.

title: WorkPackageLeader
description: Leader responsible for a specific work package in a project.
